{"id": "chos043", "name": "Cam_CArea_702_11_08", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "This is S. I'm in.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>I see your position on the map now. Turn right at the next intersection. Open the second door. You'll see a LE-113A drone inside.</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_shot_silencer", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>Nice shot. I expect no less for someone hired by the Cafe.</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Having such a detailed understanding of the underground passages in the restricted area, you're not too bad yourself either.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>*Chuckles* I appreciate your comments.</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Will we really reach Simon's cell by going down this way?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>No need to worry, trust me. Later, there will be a brief moment with no signal. Therefore, you'll need to follow my instructions.</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... I'm curious. If you know the topography down here so well, why hire a gunman? Why don't you just do it yourself?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>Hmm... Perhaps I'm currently in a situation where I can't quite move around easily, or perhaps I feel like things are more interesting this way. Who knows?</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>Isn't this great for you though? Don't you want to save him yourself? Miss Pauline?</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!? How did you know my name?\nHey? Hello...?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Damnit, signal lost.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "This is it. Password lock... Simon, I'll be there in a minute.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "Alarm"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Control System]"], "content": "<i>Decision: Incorrect password. Defense system activate. Deploy model LE-113C security drones to perform full area scan. Law enforcement agents, please leave this area as soon as possible.</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "The password is incorrect!?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Control System]"], "content": "<i>Model LE-113C security drones, deploy start.</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... We're tricked.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switch]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Drone]"], "content": "<i>Target acquired. Initiate termination process immediately.</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "S***! It's a dead end!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Drone]"], "content": "<i>Target acquired. Initiate termination process immediately.</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Tch...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>This is R. Woah, looks like it's quite the spectacle on your side of things.</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You bastard! How dare you trick me! Where the f*** am I at right now!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>No need to worry. I've already opened Simon's cell door. However, it seems like he doesn't really want to come out.</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon]"], "content": "<i>Sherry!? What are you doing here?</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>As you just saw, your dear friends are literally risking their lives for you. All in all, I will leave the door open for you, the door to end this entire fiasco. The rest is up to you.\nFeels like your dear friends are in a pretty serious pinch. Allow me to take my leave first.</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "Explosion"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">WAAA!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Thanks for the hard work, Miss Pauline.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos4301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "All clear. Let's go. The operation is over.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You...!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Yikes... K270? So you held on for so long using that piece of junk? Impressive, I should give you some bonus payment.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... The agents back there, as well as the password... You used us!\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Things crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "First, I \"hired\" you folks. Not quite \"used\".\nSecond, From start to finish, I never mentioned anything about you meeting Simon. Seems like it's just your own misunderstanding.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Thanks to you folks, I was able to move around easily... Both you and the Cafe's successor have outperformed my expectations significantly. Praiseworthy indeed.\nThird, when pointing the K270 at someone, don't do it from the front...\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "Dismantles gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "This toy crumbles with the slightest touch.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You... just who exactly are you? Why are you saving Simon? If you're trying to harm him...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Not the smartest question, young lady.\nIf I want to cause him harm, I would've already dragged him out of there. I wouldn't leave him in there to make a \"choice\". This choice is essential in determining whether or not he is qualified to be my comrade.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Drone]"], "content": "<i>Target acquired. Initiate termination process immediately.</i>\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Chit-chat time over. You don't have that worthless gun anymore. Follow me if you don't want to die. We still got one more person to rescue.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "こちらS。侵入成功。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>あぁ、君の位置はマップで確認できている。\nその先を右折して、2つ目の扉だ。\n扉を開けると、中にはLE-113A 型のドローンがいる。</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_shot_silencer", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>いい腕だ。\nさすがCafeが探してきた人材だな。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "管制区の地下通路をここまで調べられるなんて、あんたもなかなかやるね。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>ははは！それほどでも。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "このまま進めば、本当にSimonのところまでたどり着けるんだよね？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>安心して任せてくれたまえ。\nこの先しばらく電波の繋がらない場所がある。\n私の指示をよく聞くんだ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……なんで、自分で来ないわけ？\nここの内部の作りにそれだけ詳しければ、わざわざ誰かを雇う必要はないでしょ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>ふむ……\n私はあまり好き勝手に身動きが取れない状況に身を置いているから……\nいや、もしかすると、この方が面白いからかもしれない……\n真相は誰にも分からんよ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>君にとってもこの方がいいのではないかね？\n君自身、彼を自らの手で救い出したいと願っているのだろう？ん？Miss Pauline？</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！？なんであたしの名前を！\nもしもし、もしもし……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……くそ！電波が切れたんだ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "焦った足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ここだ。\nパスワードロック……\nSimon、今助けるから。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警報"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[管制システム]"], "content": "<i>Decision：パスワードが違います。\n防御システム作動。\nLE-113C型警備ドローン配置。\n全区域にてスキャン開始。\n執法員は速やかに該当エリアを離れてください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "パスワードが違う！？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[管制システム]"], "content": "<i>LE-113C型警備ドローン配置完了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……はめられた。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ドローン]"], "content": "<i>ターゲットを確認。\n殲滅を開始します。</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "焦った足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "しまった！行き止まりだ！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ドローン]"], "content": "<i>ターゲットを確認。\n殲滅を開始します。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……っく！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>こちらR。\nおや、面白いことになっているようだね。</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ペテン師め！騙したな！\n今どこにいやがる！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>まあまあ、そう怒らないでくれたまえ。\n私は今Simonの部屋の扉を開けたところさ。\n本人はあまり出てきたくなさそうだがね。</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon]"], "content": "<i>Sherry！？お前何して……！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>君の見た通りさ。\n仲間たちは今君のために命をはっている。\nとにかく、この騒ぎをおさめるための扉はもう開いた。\nあとは、君がどうするかだ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆破"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">うわ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "ご苦労さん、Miss Pauline。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos4301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "片付いたぞ。行こう。\nミッションは完了だ。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "てめぇ……！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おや……これはK270かな？\nこんなボロで今まで戦ってたのかね？\n報酬をもっと渡すべきだったな。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……さっきの執法員といい、パスワードといい……\nあたしらを利用したな！？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "まず第一に、私は君たちを「雇用」したのであって、利用したのではない……\n次に、私は君がSimonに会えるとは言っていない。\n君が勝手に誤解したのだろう。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "君たちのおかげで、動きやすかったよ……\n君も、Cafeの2代目も、私の期待以上の働きをしてくれた。\n称賛に値するだろう。\nそして、K270を他人に向ける時は、正面から突き付けるのはやめた方がいい……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "銃を解体する"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "その玩具は少し触れただけで壊れてしまうからな。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あんた……何者？\nなんでSimonを助けた？\nもしあいつに何かするつもりなら……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "その問題は、あまり頭のいい質問ではないな。\nもし私が彼に対して何らかの不利益となりうる行為をするつもりであれば、私は彼をあそこから引きずり出していただろう。\n彼に「選択肢」を与えたりせずにな。\nあの選択は、彼が私の仲間としてふさわしいか否かを見定めるための試練だったのだよ。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ドローン]"], "content": "<i>ターゲットを確認。\n殲滅を開始します。</i>\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おしゃべりはこれくらいにしておこう。\n君のボロはもうお陀仏だ。\n死にたくなければ、私と共に来るといい。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "這裡是 S，我進來了。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>我在地圖上看到妳的位置了，待會前面右轉，開第二個門。裡面會有一台 LE-113A 型的無人機。</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_shot_silencer", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>好槍法，不愧是 Cafe 找來的人啊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "能把管制區的地下通道調查得那麼清楚，你也很不簡單。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>呵呵，過獎。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "再往前走真的能通到 Simon 的牢房嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>放心交給我吧，待會會有一段路收不到訊號，妳聽我的指示做。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我很好奇，既然對地形瞭若指掌，為什麼要請槍手，不親自出馬？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>嗯……或許我現在正處於一個不太方便行動的狀態，又或許我覺得這樣比較有趣，誰知道呢？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>這不是很好嗎？難道妳不想親自救他嗎？Miss Pauline？</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！？你怎麼知道我的名字？\n喂？喂……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……可惡，斷訊了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "到了，密碼鎖……Simon，我馬上就來。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警報"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[管制系統]"], "content": "<i>判定：密碼錯誤，啟動防禦系統，投入 LE-113C 型警備無人機進行全域掃描，執法員請儘速離開本區域。</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "密碼是錯的！？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[管制系統]"], "content": "<i>LE-113C 警備無人機，投放開始。</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……上當了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>發現目標，即刻進行殲滅動作。</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "糟糕，是死路！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>發現目標，即刻進行殲滅動作。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>這裡是 R。哇，妳那兒看起來很精彩啊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你這混蛋！居然騙我！我現在到底在哪！？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>別緊張，我已經把 Simon 的房門打開了，不過他好像不太願意出來啊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon]"], "content": "<i>Sherry！？妳在這做什麼？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>就像你看到的，小夥伴們在為了你拼命啊。總之，結束這場鬧劇的大門我幫你開著了，剩下的就看你自己了。\n你的小夥伴們感覺不太妙呢，我先告辭了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆破"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "辛苦妳了，Miss Pauline。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos4301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "清光了。走吧，行動結束了。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你……！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哇……K270？虧妳能用這種破槍撐到現在啊，該多付點錢給妳呢。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……剛剛的執法員，還有密碼……你利用我們！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "第一、我是「僱用」你們，並不是利用。\n第二、我從頭到尾沒有說過妳會與 Simon 碰面，看樣子是妳自己誤會了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "多虧了你們，讓我可以方便行動……妳和 Cafe 的第二代，表現都遠超我的預期，值得嘉許。\n第三、用 K270 抵著別人的時候不要從正面……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "拆解槍枝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這玩意一碰就散了。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你……到底是誰？為什麼要救 Simon？如果是想對他不利……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這問題不太聰明呢。我如果想對他不利，早就把他拖出來了，不會把他留在那裡做「選擇」。這個選擇關乎到他有沒有資格成為我的同伴。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>發現目標，即刻進行殲滅動作。</i>\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "閒聊時間結束。妳的破槍沒了，不想死就跟上我吧，我們還有一個人要救呢。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "여기는 S. 침입에 성공했다.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>위치 확인했습니다. 앞에서 우회전한 뒤, 두 번째 문을 열면 안에 LE-113A형 드론이 한 기 있을 겁니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_shot_silencer", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>멋진 솜씨로군요. 역시 Cafe가 추천한 인재 답습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "관제 구역 지하 통로에 대해서도 아주 제대로 조사했던데, 당신도 예사 인물은 아니군.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>하하하! 과찬이십니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "다시 앞으로 전진하면 Simon이 있는 방에 도달할 수 있다고 했지?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>안심하셔도 좋습니다. 중간에 신호 차단 구역이 나올 텐데 그때 잠깐 연락이 끊길 겁니다. 그전까지 제 지시대로 해주시면 됩니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...갑자기 궁금한 게 생겼어. 지형을 이렇게까지 완벽하게 파악하고 있으면서 어째서 직접 나서지 않고 총잡이를 구한 거지?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>흐음... 아마 제가 직접 움직이기 곤란한 상황이기 때문일 수도 있고, 아니면 이쪽 편이 더 재밌을 것 같아 그런 걸 수도 있고, 뭐, 진실은 아무도 모를 겁니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>이쪽 편이 더 낫다고 생각 안 하십니까? 직접 자신의 손으로 그 친구를 구하고 싶었을 텐데 말이죠, Miss Pauline?</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...!? 어떻게 내 이름을?\n여보세요? 여보세...?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...제길. 전파가 약해졌어.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "도착했다!\n비밀번호가.... 좋았어.\nSimon, 금방 갈게.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "경보음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[관제 시스템]"], "content": "<i>판정: 비밀번호 오류. 방어 시스템을 가동합니다. LE-113C형 경비 드론을 투입하여 전구역 스캐닝을 시작할 예정이오니, 해당 구역의 집법원들은 신속히 이곳을 떠나주시기 바랍니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "틀린 비밀번호라니!?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[관제 시스템]"], "content": "<i>LE-113C형 경비 드론 투입, 개시.</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...날 속였어...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[드론]"], "content": "<i>목표 발견. \n즉시 목표를 제거합니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "큰일이다! 막힌 길이야!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[드론]"], "content": "<i>목표 발견. \n즉시 목표를 제거합니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "윽...!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>여기는 R.\n와우, 그쪽은 매우 재밌어진 것 같군요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "이 x자식! 날 속이다니! 지금 여긴 대체 어디야!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>이런, 긴장할 필요 없습니다. 전 이미 Simon의 방으로 들어왔습니다. 그런데 이 친구가 별로 나가고 싶어 하지 않는 것 같군요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon]"], "content": "<i>Sherry!? \n네가 왜 여기에!?</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>보시는 것처럼,\n동료들이 당신을 위해 목숨을 걸었습니다. 어쨌든, 당신이 이 소동으로부터 빠져나갈 수 있는 문은 모두 준비된 셈이군요. 나머지는 당신에게 달렸습니다.\n그런데 지금, 당신 동료가 약간 난처한 상황에 처한 것 같습니다만? \n그럼 전 이만.</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "폭발"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">으앗!</font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "수고했습니다, Miss Pauline.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos4301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "깔끔하군요. 이제 갑시다.\n할 일은 이제 모두 끝낸 것 같으니.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "네 녀석....!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "오호... K270라니?\n용케도 이런 장난감으로 지금까지 잘 버티셨군요. 이거, 보수를 더 드려야 할 것 같은데.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...방금 집법원도 그렇고... 그리고 비밀번호도... 우리를 이용했어!\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "첫 번째, 전 여러분을 「고용」한 것이지 이용한 게 아닙니다.\n두 번째, 전 단 한 번도 당신이 Simon과 만나게 될 것이라고 말한 적이 없습니다만. 당신이 뭔가 오해를 한 것 같군요.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "고생 많았습니다. 여러분 덕택에 어렵지 않게 움직일 수 있었습니다. 당신과 Cafe의 2대, 모두 기대 이상으로 훌륭하게 해내주었습니다.\n그리고 마지막으로 세 번째.\nK270로 목표를 겨냥할 땐 정면으로 조준하지 말라고 말씀드리고 싶군요. 그렇지 않으면...\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "총기를 해체한다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이런 장난감은 이렇게 순식간에 분해되버리고 말거든요.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "당신... 대체 정체가 뭐야? 어째서 Simon을 구하려고 하는 거지? 만약 그 녀석에게 무슨 일이라도 생긴다면...\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "참 바보 같은 질문이로군요. 만약 그 친구에게 해가 될 일을 하려 했다면, 진작에 「선택지」같은 걸 주지도 않았을 겁니다. 그 선택지는 나의 동료가 될 수 있는 자격 여부에 관련된 것이기도 하죠.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[드론]"], "content": "<i>목표 발견. 즉시 제거를 시작합니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "한가한 얘기는 여기까지인 것 같군요. 당신의 장난감도 고장 나버렸으니, 죽고 싶지 않다면 절 따라오시죠. 아직 구해야 할 사람이 1명 더 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "這裡是 S，我進來了。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>我在地圖上看到妳的位置了，待會前面右轉，開第二個門。裡面會有一台 LE-113A 型的無人機。</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_shot_silencer", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>好槍法，不愧是 Cafe 找來的人啊。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "能把管制區的地下通道調查得那麼清楚，你也很不簡單。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>呵呵，過獎。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "再往前走真的能通到 Simon 的牢房嗎？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>放心交給我吧，待會會有一段路收不到訊號，妳聽我的指示做。</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我很好奇，既然對地形瞭若指掌，為什麼要請槍手，不親自出馬？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>嗯……或許我現在正處於一個不太方便行動的狀態，又或許我覺得這樣比較有趣，誰知道呢？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>這不是很好嗎？難道妳不想親自救他嗎？Miss Pauline？</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！？你怎麼知道我的名字？\n喂？喂……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……可惡，斷訊了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "c