 ["GunShot_03", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "辛苦妳了，Miss Pauline。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos4301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "清光了。走吧，行動結束了。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你……！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哇……K270？虧妳能用這種破槍撐到現在啊，該多付點錢給妳呢。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……剛剛的執法員，還有密碼……你利用我們！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "第一、我是「僱用」你們，並不是利用。\n第二、我從頭到尾沒有說過妳會與 Simon 碰面，看樣子是妳自己誤會了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "多虧了你們，讓我可以方便行動……妳和 Cafe 的第二代，表現都遠超我的預期，值得嘉許。\n第三、用 K270 抵著別人的時候不要從正面……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "拆解槍枝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這玩意一碰就散了。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你……到底是誰？為什麼要救 Simon？如果是想對他不利……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這問題不太聰明呢。我如果想對他不利，早就把他拖出來了，不會把他留在那裡做「選擇」。這個選擇關乎到他有沒有資格成為我的同伴。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>發現目標，即刻進行殲滅動作。</i>\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "閒聊時間結束。妳的破槍沒了，不想死就跟上我吧，我們還有一個人要救呢。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "这里是 S，我进来了。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>我在地图上看到妳的位置了，待会前面右转，开第二个门。里面会有一台 LE-113A 型的无人机。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_shot_silencer", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>好枪法，不愧是 Cafe 找来的人啊。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "能把管制区的地下通道调查得那么清楚，你也很不简单。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>呵呵，过奖。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "再往前走真的能通到 Simon 的牢房吗？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>放心交给我吧，待会会有一段路收不到讯号，妳听我的指示做。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我很好奇，既然对地形了若指掌，为什么要请枪手，不亲自出马？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>嗯……或许我现在正处于一个不太方便行动的状态，又或许我觉得这样比较有趣，谁知道呢？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>这不是很好吗？难道妳不想亲自救他吗？ Miss Pauline？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！ ？你怎么知道我的名字？\n喂？喂……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……可恶，断讯了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "到了，密码锁……Simon，我马上就来。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Alarm_2", "警报"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！ ？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[管制系统]"], "content": "<i>判定：密码错误，启动防御系统，投入 LE-113C 型警备无人机进行全域扫描，执法员请尽速离开本区域。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "密码是错的！ ？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[管制系统]"], "content": "<i>LE-113C 警备无人机，投放开始。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……上当了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[无人机]"], "content": "<i>发现目标，即刻进行歼灭动作。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "糟糕，是死路！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[无人机]"], "content": "<i>发现目标，即刻进行歼灭动作。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>这里是 R。哇，妳那儿看起来很精彩啊。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你这混蛋！居然骗我！我现在到底在哪！ ？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>别紧张，我已经把 Simon 的房门打开了，不过他好像不太愿意出来啊。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon]"], "content": "<i>Sherry！ ？妳在这做什么？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Rald]"], "content": "<i>就像你看到的，小伙伴们在为了你拼命啊。总之，结束这场闹剧的大门我帮你开着了，剩下的就看你自己了。\n你的小伙伴们感觉不太妙呢，我先告辞了。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆破"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇！ ？ </font>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "辛苦妳了，Miss Pauline。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos4301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "清光了。走吧，行动结束了。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你……！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哇……K270？亏妳能用这种破枪撑到现在啊，该多付点钱给妳呢。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……刚刚的执法员，还有密码……你利用我们！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "第一、我是「雇用」你们，并不是利用。\n第二、我从头到尾没有说過妳会与 Simon 碰面，看样子是妳自己误会了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "多亏了你们，让我可以方便行动……妳和 Cafe 的第二代，表现都远超我的预期，值得嘉许。\n第三、用 K270 抵着别人的时候不要从正面……\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "拆解枪枝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "这玩意一碰就散了。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你……到底是谁？为什么要救 Simon？如果是想对他不利……\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "这问题不太聪明呢。我如果想对他不利，早就把他拖出来了，不会把他留在那里做「选择」。这个选择关乎到他有没有资格成为我的同伴。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[无人机]"], "content": "<i>发现目标，即刻进行歼灭动作。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "闲聊时间结束。妳的破枪没了，不想死就跟上我吧，我们还有一个人要救呢。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}